{"tid":2300453,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"讀緊乞食社科可以做啲咩增加自己嘅競爭力？","createTime":"2020-11-25T13:55:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-26T11:01:33.000Z","uid":368023,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"9d1bc124da1ca04907ba558d7ec4cf536f04de30","tid":2300453,"uid":368023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T13:55:54.000Z","msg":"如題 <br />\n宜家year1 讀緊三大乞食社科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好擔心未來要乞食<br />\n自問英文能力唔差，宜家有學緊外語<br />\n<br />\n本身自己讀緊嗰科，有唔少師兄師姐grad咗都係做LS老師，本身自己都打算之後考牌做老師就算<br />\n但見到今日柒婆份施政報告即刻9秒9打消咗呢個諗法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n交jupas之前睇過好多連登勸世po, 叫人點都一定要揀專科，但自己都仲係on99咁揀咗sosci入面差唔多最乞食嗰科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n宜家好驚第時真係要乞食，想知可以點樣先增加到自己嘅競爭力，至少唔好第日交cv就第一時間比人screen走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔該曬咁多位巴絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/adore_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/adore_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/adore_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw如果有中學生睇到呢個po, 有得選擇嘅話真係記得要揀專科呀 唔好好似我咁on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbeea51cf65ada01f7d16a6d65537a0ba188121b","tid":2300453,"uid":375055,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{